---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 245
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Judgement=On Judging Others
By: Peter Sterry
---
If thou art an Angel, and hath to do with a Devil, use no reviling
Language, for so the Angel himself is by the Spirit of God markt with
a Character of Honour for this, that he used no reviling Speeches to
the Devil.
